<h2>Help & Instructions</h2>

<p>
    Need assistance using the <strong>Fitness & Calorie Tracker</strong>? Here’s how to navigate each subsystem:
</p>

<ol>
    <li><strong>User Profile:</strong> Create or edit your personal information and daily calorie goal.</li>
    <li><strong>Calorie Tracking:</strong> Log meals and track your daily calorie intake.</li>
    <li><strong>Workout Tracking:</strong> Record workouts and calories burned.</li>
    <li><strong>Daily Summary:</strong> View your total calories consumed and burned for the day.</li>
    <li><strong>Reminders:</strong> Set reminders for workouts or meal logging.</li>
</ol>

<p>
    For technical issues, contact your instructor or refer to the project documentation.
</p>

